7
00:00:25.980 --> 00:00:30.200
It is a Tuesday morning in the barbecue
capital of the world.

8
00:00:30.800 --> 00:00:32.640
That's right, Kansas City.

9
00:00:33.024 --> 00:00:37.704
A landlord named David wakes up, and before
his feet hit the floor, he is already

10
