25
00:01:32.500 --> 00:01:37.800
If only I had known the reality of being a
landlord, I might have made a different choice.

27
00:01:37.800 --> 00:01:40.800
David is not a bad landlord.

28
00:01:41.380 --> 00:01:47.340
He is a tired one, and he has been carrying
this property like a weight around his neck.

29
00:01:48.640 --> 00:01:53.280
Or picture Beth. She is an executor of her
mother's estate in St.

30
